{"calories":"880","carbs":105,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eCavatappi, a ridged, corkscrew-shaped pasta, is excellent for holding the sauce in this vegetarian dish. Sun-dried tomatoes, sautéed with aromatics and plumped in white wine, add an intense sweet-and-tangy flavor to the cream sauce. Earthy roasted shiitake and cremini mushrooms balance the sauce. Dollop over the whipped ricotta for a luxurious finish. \u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"5e539e4e3c","fat":38,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55519/large_cropped_CJuqjKE8Q9idFTRh6O5c_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55518/tZKQ9aQSXi4LGXlv6ANe_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0026___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55518/menu_small_tZKQ9aQSXi4LGXlv6ANe_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0026___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55517/L9rsbQBjTNmG9dzY9PsJ_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0030___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55516/UNC1p8bSGPRFo0GrVDQg_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55516/hero_UNC1p8bSGPRFo0GrVDQg_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55516/menu_small_UNC1p8bSGPRFo0GrVDQg_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55516/small_square_UNC1p8bSGPRFo0GrVDQg_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55516/medium_square_UNC1p8bSGPRFo0GrVDQg_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55516/recipe_profile_page_UNC1p8bSGPRFo0GrVDQg_Mushroom_Cavatappi_with_Creamy_Sun-Dried_Tomato_Sauce-0028___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}}],"name":"Mushroom Cavatappi with Creamy Sun-Dried Tomato Sauce","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":24,"public_slug":"creamy-pappardelle-with-funghi-and-ricotta","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/37237/recipe_card20180928-11-zmko6d.pdf","recipe_id":5674,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Mushroom Cavatappi","subtitle":"with Creamy Sun-Dried Tomato Sauce","title":"Mushroom Cavatappi","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you\u0026#x27;ll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eHere’s a cheffy trick for picking thyme leaves all at once: Pinch the stem near the top with 1 hand, then slide the fingers of your other hand down the length of the stem, from top to bottom. The leaves will come off easily.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the remaining pasta cooking water to the pot 1 tablespoon at a time until the sauce reaches your desired consistency (you likely won\u0026#x27;t use all of the water). \u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","aluminum foil","baking sheet"],"id":5674,"ingredients":["shiitake mushrooms","cremini mushrooms","sun-dried tomatoes","shallot","garlic","cavatappi","ricotta cheese","white wine","heavy cream","chives","thyme"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"shiitake mushrooms","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/221/medium_square_shiitake-mushrooms-test.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"sun-dried tomatoes","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2071/medium_square_sundried-tomatoes.jpg"},{"name":"shallot","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/130/medium_square_SHALLOT_copy.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"cavatappi","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2357/medium_square_2018-05-24___DS_18279079.jpg"},{"name":"ricotta cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1486/medium_square_RICOTTA_CHEESE_-4386_copy.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"heavy cream","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"container","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2301/medium_square_HEAVY_CREAM_copy.jpg"},{"name":"chives","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1281/medium_square_medium_square_chives-2-test.jpg"},{"name":"thyme","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1289/medium_square_medium_square_herb-thyme-fresh.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55570/recipe_card_size_I2gVJwxCQHOnW8mN9hVz_1._Prepare_ingredients_1.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003emushroom\u003c/strong\u003e stems, wipe caps clean with a damp paper towel, and cut into .25-inch slices. Rinse remaining produce. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003echives\u003c/strong\u003e. Roughly chop \u003cstrong\u003esun-dried tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eshallot\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast mushrooms","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55572/recipe_card_size_v1xn5tfPSo6yZxm9heXw_3._Roast_mushrooms_and_season_ricotta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eLine a baking sheet with foil. Set aside \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of whole thyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e, then strip leaves of \u003cstrong\u003eremainder \u003c/strong\u003efor ricotta, discarding stems (see recipe tip). Add \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ewhole\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ethyme sprigs \u003c/strong\u003eto sheet and toss with \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. Arrange in a single layer, spacing apart, and roast until lightly browned, 12-15 minutes. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook cavatappi and season ricotta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55579/recipe_card_size_8WosedyyQxm69lQgD0TX_2._Cook_cavatappi.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile mushrooms roast, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003ecavatappi\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 7 minutes. Reserve\u003cstrong\u003e .5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, then drain and set aside until Step 6, reserving pot for making sauce. Meanwhile, in a small bowl, whisk together \u003cstrong\u003ericotta\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ethyme leaves\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e .125 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. Set aside until Step 6.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté aromatics","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55576/recipe_card_size_7L3BiPHCRa2PbpQeXwuu_4.Saute__aromatics.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003ein pot from pasta over medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003esun-dried tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eshallot\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired. Sauté, stirring, until fragrant, 2-3 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ewhite wine\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring constantly, until sun-dried tomatoes are tender and wine is mostly evaporated, 1-2 minutes more. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish sun-dried tomato sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55590/recipe_card_size_PGFwLMFCSyKTdhwcASEq_5._Finish_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003ecream\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003e.25 cup pasta cooking water \u003c/strong\u003eto pot with aromatics, still over medium-high heat; reserve \u003cstrong\u003eremaining pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e for the next step. Cook, stirring, until reduced by half, 2-3 minutes. Once roasted, remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ewhole thyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e from baking sheet. Add \u003cstrong\u003eroasted mushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e to pot and cook until flavors have melded, 1-2 minutes more. Remove pot from heat. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate mushroom cavatappi","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55601/recipe_card_size_0z8yaKrmSEWz54xN11OZ_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003ecavatappi \u003c/strong\u003eto pot with sauce, still off heat, and stir to coat. Adding 1 tablespoon at a time, stir in \u003cstrong\u003eremaining pasta cooking water \u003c/strong\u003euntil sauce is silky and clings to pasta (see recipe tip). Taste and add \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Divide \u003cstrong\u003emushroom cavatappi with creamy sun-dried tomato sauce\u003c/strong\u003e between serving bowls and top with \u003cstrong\u003ericotta\u003c/strong\u003e. Garnish with \u003cstrong\u003echives\u003c/strong\u003e and dig in!  \u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}